  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>All-inclusive including drinks daily from 8am to midnight</p>
<p>Hot and cold buffet breakfast until 10am and late riser continental breakfast until noon</p>
<p>Hot and cold lunch buffet from noon to 4pm</p>
<p>Snacks at the bar from 4pm to 8pm</p>
<p>Evening meal is served from 6pm to 9pm and is a Gourmet Buffet meal</p>
<p>Drinks included from 8am to midnight with an extensive choice of Austrian and international wines, draft beers, branded spirits, Prosecco and sparkling wine, various schnapps, cocktails, tea, coffee and soft drinks</p>
<p>Six-course Christmas Eve gala dinner included</p>
<p>Six-course New Year Eve gala dinner dance with live music and a bottle of Champagne included per room</p>]]></cateringDescription>
