  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Valsaa Alpinresort is a superb, all-inclusive hotel with extensive facilities, perfectly located just a couple of minutes' walk to the resort centre and Schattberg X-press lift.</p>
<h2>All inclusive</h2>
<p>The extensive all-inclusive offer will make it hard for you to leave the hotel. Drinks are included from 8pm to midnight each day which includes beers, a huge wine selection, spirits and soft drinks as you would expect - plus sparkling wines and cocktails too. Breakfast starts early and finishes late if you feel like a lie in. And is quickly followed by lunch and afternoon snacks. A gourmet buffet dinner in the evenings completes the day.</p>
<h2>AlpinSPA</h2>
<p>The huge AlpinSPA and pool areas are perfect for relaxing after skiing or if you fancy a day off the slopes. There's an outdoor heated pool connected to an indoor massage pool, outdoor hot tub, five saunas and steam rooms, plus six relaxation areas complete the experience.</p>
<h2>Rooms</h2>
<p>The hotel has traditional wood mixed with modern décor throughout. There is a choice of rooms, from standard double rooms to spacious junior suites that are perfect for families.</p>]]></description>
