  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Komfort Austrian Twin Rooms</strong> are around 26m². They have a bath or shower and a seating area. They can sleep two people and have a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Austrian Twin Rooms</strong> are around 31m² and sleep up to three using a single sofa bed or extra bed in the seating area (maximum two adults and one child to 14 years). These modern styled rooms have oak wood floors and also have a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>offer the most space at around 36m² and sleep up to four using a double sofa bed or extras beds (maximum three adults or two adults with two children). Also with a seating area and balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Cable / satellite TV</li>
<li>Minibar / fridge</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Bathrobes</li>
</ul>
